++  py
  ::  because when you're a star with 2^16 unissued
  ::  planets, a (set) is kind of lame...
  ::
  |_  a/pile
  ::                                                    ::  ++dif:py
  ++  dif                                               ::  add/remove a->b
    |=  b/pile
    ^-  (pair pile pile)
